{"tid":924594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白宮︰磋商90天無結果就開徵關稅","createTime":"2018-12-02T08:27:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T09:06:03.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"563dcd1cf9deb83c20e2bdd8afab7b8ed804bbe6","tid":924594,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T08:27:06.000Z","msg":"特朗普原定在明年1月1日將2,000億美元（約1.56萬億港元）中國貨的入口關稅，由目前的10%增至25%。白宮發言人桑德斯（Sarah Sanders）表示，特朗普已同意暫緩向中國貨加徵關稅，兩國亦即時就貿易問題、知識產權及黑客問題再磋商。<br />\n桑德斯又指，如果雙方在90天內未能達成共識，美方將實施擴大徵稅。<br />\n白宮另表示，中國已同意將向美國「購買非常大量的農業、能源、工業等產品」，以收窄美對華的貿易逆差，不過詳情未有定案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181202/58982445?fbclid=IwAR2sdWFkzGUrJIp2sFYxDwXlYOfbwuPDLXvJKJDHRoHkgAMuXJu1ItxAlQc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181202%2F58982445%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2sdWFkzGUrJIp2sFYxDwXlYOfbwuPDLXvJKJDHRoHkgAMuXJu1ItxAlQc&d=ANChfUt99FUJmRYkrR0xNsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=bd69ca31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181202%2F58982445%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2sdWFkzGUrJIp2sFYxDwXlYOfbwuPDLXvJKJDHRoHkgAMuXJu1ItxAlQc&h=c81b7716\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181202/58982445?fbclid=IwAR2sdWFkzGUrJIp2sFYxDwXlYOfbwuPDLXvJKJDHRoHkgAMuXJu1ItxAlQc</a>"},{"pid":"ba113506da8f6eabdc4ab2943546158e61dfe4fd","tid":924594,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T08:28:37.000Z","msg":"到頭來只係美國略施恩惠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9768cf66773946bc37f8a5940940bf2fbe7a337","tid":924594,"uid":179908,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T08:31:47.000Z","msg":"美國媒體最新消息：因為中國同意購買大量農業，能源，工業及其他產品，改善貿易不平衡。所以暫停增加新關稅，但協議還未达成，會在90天內繼續協商。<span style=\"color: red;\">如果未來90天未能就知識產權，網絡盜竊，技術轉讓，農業貿易各問題迖成協議，會繼續